thread.title: TV | The Muppets

author: Fiona Flynn
title: TV | The Muppets
text: At long last The Muppets are back on our telly in this much anticipated spoof documentary series which goes behind the scenes with Kermit and the gang as they produce talk show 'Up Late with Miss Piggy'. As you may have heard, Kermit and Miss Piggy split up over the summer, proving that in fact, love is dead. Kermit has even moved on now and is dating some younger pig lady called Denise... pffft. In the first episode, Kermit decides to ignore Miss PIggy's vetoing of guest Elizabeth Banks, leaving Scooter struggling to keep the Hunger Games star and the volatile host apart until they meet on stage.
